com.abbyy.mobile.rtr

Interface IDataCaptureService.Callback

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IRecognitionService.Callback
    Enclosing interface:
    IDataCaptureService

    public static interface IDataCaptureService.Callback
extends IRecognitionService.Callback
    A callback interface to interact with the data capture service: input the data and obtain the results. While the service is being stopped, frames continue to be requested and calls to this callback continue to be queued, so this callback can be called after the service has been stopped.
